         MACRO - RESERVE SPACE FOR EDIT WORK AREA ONCE ONLY
         RCPEDIT
         GBLC  &RCPPRE,&RCPEDIT
         AIF   ('&RCPEDIT' NE '').MEND
&RCPEDIT SETC  '&RCPPRE.EDIT'
         AIF   ('&RCPPRE' NE '').DS
&RCPEDIT SETC  'RCPEDIT'
.DS      RCPDS
&RCPEDIT DS    3D             EDIT MACRO WORK AREA
         RCPDS
.MEND    MEND
